{"id":331492,"type":6,"name":"蓋世豪俠","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/88/be/331492_srGRh.jpg","summary":"古峰（吴孟达 饰）和段海（刘江 饰）皆是苍穹派弟子，因为盗取了极乐神功的秘籍，古峰保住了段海，自己却被逐出师门。为了报答古峰，段海收养了他的儿子古玉楼（吴镇宇 饰），对其悉心教导，段海待古玉楼之好，甚至超过了待他的亲生儿子段飞（周星驰 饰）。 \r\n　　一晃眼数年过去，古玉楼和段飞都成长为了壮硕的青年，然而两人的个性却截然相反。古玉楼个性桀骜不驯，自高自大，唯我独尊，为了达到目的不择手段，更为了称霸武林而修炼邪派武功，最终沦落至走火入魔的境地。段飞尽管淡泊名利，只想过安稳生活，却屡屡被卷入江湖的纷争之中，自己的父亲更是死在了古玉楼的手上，段飞决心替父报仇。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>盖世豪侠</li><li><span>主演: </span><a href=\"/person/17882\">羅慧娟</a>、<a href=\"/person/17423\">周星馳</a>、<a href=\"/person/17561\">藍潔瑛</a>、<a href=\"/person/16642\">吳孟達</a>、<a href=\"/person/16700\">吳鎮宇</a></li><li><span>制作: </span><a href=\"/person/38099\">TVB</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>The Final Combat</li><li><span>集数: </span>30</li><li><span>开始: </span>1989-04-03</li><li><span>类型: </span>动作</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>中国香港</li><li><span>语言: </span>广东话</li>","eps":[{"id":1017349,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1017349","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":1017350,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1017350","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":1017351,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1017351","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":1017352,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1017352","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":1017353,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1017353","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":1017354,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1017354","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":1017355,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1017355","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":1017356,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/101